{
  "stem": "444.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I told him that, he said, you are a German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, I will release you, but I want you to disappear in 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So he gave me a piece of paper, and they took me back to the cell, and about an hour later, somebody came, opened the door, and said, you're going out.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there nine months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So when I went out, two girls came to me outside of the prison.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took me under their arm, and took me to their home, where I could get-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I got a toothbrush and soap so I could wash myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't know them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were girls from the underground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What makes me think-- there are two things that could happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why there were no-- no record of me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Perhaps the underground somehow got my records out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's one possibility.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other possibility is that-- that my aunt sent a German officer whom she knew from the town of [NON-ENGLISH], which is in the northern part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He-- he was going to Sanok to see if he can get my release.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He came home and-- came home and told my aunt that there was no way that I could be released.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was probably was designed to be shot like the other guys, however something happened, and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I got out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I got out, I went to the town of Lublin, where my brother lived-- older brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And from that town, we went to a small town, not a small--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
